thumb|200px|left|A Sirius Cybernetics Corporation robot.
A robot is a mechanical or virtual artificial agent, usually an electro-mechanical machine that is guided by a computer program or electronic circuitry. The Encyclopedia Galactica defines a robot as "a mechanical apparatus designed to do the work of a man." The marketing division of the Sirius Cybernetics Corporation defines a robot as "Your Plastic Pal Who's Fun To Be With."From the Douglas Adams book The Hitchhiker's Guide to the Galaxy
thumb|104px|Marvin, the best-known robot from Hitchhiker.
Many robots are featured in the Hitchhiker's universe, including:
Marvin
Colin the Security Robot
The Krikkit War Robots